EncounterParticipantGivenNameSearchParameter

Parameter participant.given:string

Searches for Encounters based on the Practitioner's given name(s) eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Encounter?participant.given={givenName}

ResourceEncounter
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesEncounter
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
